scripts.dev: echo "Please use 'pnpm run dev:esm' and note that it's only possible to build the ESM version of the package this way."; exit 1
scripts.prepublishOnly: pnpm run lint && pnpm run build && pnpm run test
scripts.docs: jsdoc2md --template jsdoc2md/README.hbs --files ./*.[c]js -g grouped --separators | sed '/\*\*Kind\*\*/d' | sed '/## $/d' | sed 's/## \([a-z]\)/### \1/' > README.md && node jsdoc2md/fixSorting.cjs
